text: Fans noticed the reality star dad attending a concert this past weekend. The account that shared the photos wrote, ` ` Anyone see this? It ’ s Tyler at a concert last night. Caught doing what? Talking to a 50 year old grandma who is a fan of the show? Yeah I guess I ’ m'busted'lol.'' Adding, ` ` You people just refuse to believe in a faithful relationship.
